Title: Non-Abelian Chern-Simons Quantum Mechanics
Authors: Taejin Lee and Phillial Oh
Comments: 11 pages, SNUTP-93-4
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 72 (1994) 1141-1144
\\
  We propose a classical model for the non-Abelian Chern-Simons theory coupled
to $N$ point-like sources and quantize the system using the BRST technique. The
resulting quantum mechanics provides a unified framework for fractional spin,
braid statistics and Knizhnik-Zamolodchikov equation.
